<gco:CharacterString>This is the Ozark - St. Francis National Forests Wild and Scenic River Cooridor polygon layer. In Apil 1992, Congress designated six Wild and Scenic Rivers on the Ozark - St. Francis National Forests. These rivers include: Big Piney Creek, the Buffalo River, Hurricane Creek, Mulberry River, North Sylamore Creek and Richland Creek. These areas include approximately 19,859 acres of the Ozark - St. Francis National Forests. This MA is unsuitable for timber prduction. The total miles of Wild and Scenic River designation is 162.5 miles.</gco:CharacterString>          </gmd:abstract>          <gmd:purpose>             <gco:CharacterString>Ozark National Forest uses this data to determine location of Wild & Scenic Rivers on the forest.</gco:CharacterString>          </gmd:purpose>          <gmd:status>             <gmd:MD_ProgressCode codeList="http://www.isotc211.org/2005/resources/Codelist/gmxCodelists.xml#MD_ProgressCode"                                  codeListValue="completed">completed</gmd:MD_ProgressCode>          </gmd:status>          <gmd:pointOfContact>             <gmd:CI_ResponsibleParty>                <gmd:individualName>                   <gco:CharacterString>Tammy Hocut</gco:CharacterString>                </gmd:individualName>                <gmd:organisationName>                   <gco:CharacterString>USDA Forest Service - Ozark - St. Francis National Forest</gco:CharacterString>                </gmd:organisationName>                <gmd:positionName>                   <gco:CharacterString>Forest GIS Coordinator</gco:CharacterString>                </gmd:positionName>                <gmd:contactInfo>                   <gmd:CI_Contact>                      <gmd:phone>                         <gmd:CI_Telephone>                            <gmd:voice>                               <gco:CharacterString>479-964-7211</gco:CharacterString>                            </gmd:voice>                            <gmd:facsimile>                               <gco:CharacterString>479-964-7255</gco:CharacterString>                            </gmd:facsimile>                         </gmd:CI_Telephone>                      </gmd:phone>                      <gmd:address>                         <gmd:CI_Address>                            <gmd:deliveryPoint>                               <gco:CharacterString>605 W.
